data.description: Fairly new community, serene surrounding Come see this home Better than new it has upgraded tile floors and custom shelves. Spacious M/B closet double sinks family room and kitchen combination for that open space feeling yet is cozy to entertain. The loft can be used as a playroom or office. SAVE on electricity Leased Solar Panels, community club house has a gym fully equipped. Also, the pool has jacuzzi and a sauna. Near the park Mt views and is next to diamond valley lake and the wildflower trail.              PRICE REDUCE
